
% spherepop.typing - Typing judgments (inference rule notation)

(T-Sphere)
---------------------------
Γ ⊢ σ : Sphere

(T-Policy)
---------------------------
Γ ⊢ π : Policy

(T-Apply)
Γ ⊢ π : Policy     Γ ⊢ σ : Sphere
----------------------------------
Γ ⊢ π(σ) : Sphere

(T-Merge)
Γ ⊢ σ1 : Sphere    Γ ⊢ σ2 : Sphere
----------------------------------
Γ ⊢ σ1 merge σ2 : Sphere

(Entropy-Budget)
Γ ⊢ σ : Sphere
ΔE(π,σ) ≤ Budget(σ)
-------------------------
Γ ⊢ π : Policy [budget-sound]
